1
00:00:04,000 --> 00:00:07,500
Hey, can I talk to you about something today?

2
00:00:09,000 --> 00:00:12,500
Of course. What's going on?

3
00:00:14,000 --> 00:00:17,500
Actually, I haven't been getting along with my parents lately.

4
00:00:19,500 --> 00:00:23,000
I see. Did something happen?

5
00:00:24,500 --> 00:00:28,000
They're against my modeling career. They keep telling me to get a stable job.

6
00:00:30,000 --> 00:00:33,500
Parents do worry, don't they? But I understand how you feel, Mai.

7
00:00:35,500 --> 00:00:39,000
Thanks. It means a lot to have someone who understands.

8
00:00:41,000 --> 00:00:44,500
Actually, I've been struggling with family stuff too.

9
00:00:46,500 --> 00:00:50,000
Wait, really? You too, Daiki?

10
00:00:51,500 --> 00:00:55,000
Yeah. My father is a strict person. He barely ever praised me growing up.

11
00:00:57,000 --> 00:01:00,500
That must be tough. But I think you're a really kind person, Daiki.

12
00:01:02,500 --> 00:01:06,000
I've been thinking lately, isn't it hard to like yourself?

13
00:01:08,000 --> 00:01:11,500
Yeah, it is. But I think we can change little by little.

14
00:01:13,500 --> 00:01:17,000
Maybe it was a good idea to come to this house. Because we can have talks like this.

15
00:01:19,000 --> 00:01:22,500
We don't usually get to have conversations like these, do we?

16
00:01:24,500 --> 00:01:28,000
I realized that everyone has their own worries.

17
00:01:30,000 --> 00:01:33,500
But having a place where you can talk about them is important, right?

18
00:01:35,500 --> 00:01:39,000
Yeah. I don't want to keep everything bottled up inside.

19
00:01:41,000 --> 00:01:44,500
If anything comes up, tell me anytime. I'll listen.

20
00:01:46,500 --> 00:01:50,000
Thank you. Really, thank you.
